  "detailed_description": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/793720/extras/banner_gif.png?t=1523708312\" ><br>' U L T R A _ H A R D C O R E ' is an ultra hard game to complete.<br>Challenge the Impossible and become the Winner!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Will Your Brain Handle This?</strong></h2>The game is based on a mechanic of performing two different actions at once:<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Typing a word with your left hand</li><li>Preventing filling of the red zones with your right hand</li></ul>This means that you won't have enough time to complete hard stages doing the actions consecutively, rather you will have to perform the actions simultaneously.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Simple Controls</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><i>Alphabet keys</i> for word typing<br></li><li><i>Arrow keys</i> for the zones<br></li><li><i>Alt</i> and <i>F4</i></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Try Your Luck With In-Game Item Drops</strong></h2><br>Lots of unique items are dropping during your playtime<br><strong>Important Note:</strong> Those items have no value in-game for now. It should be considered as an appreciation for supporting the game<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Achievements</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Alphabet Achievements made in game's style, which can be unlocked during your in-game progress<br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/793720/extras/Y.png?t=1523708312\" > <img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/793720/extras/E.png?t=1523708312\" > <img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/793720/extras/A.png?t=1523708312\" > <img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/793720/extras/H.png?t=1523708312\" ><br></li><li>And lots of secret ones, so you'll have to think about how to get them<br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/793720/extras/ach_lock.png?t=1523708312\" > <img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/793720/extras/0.png?t=1523708312\" > <img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/793720/extras/11.png?t=1523708312\" > <img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/793720/extras/ach_lock.png?t=1523708312\" ></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Credits</strong></h2>Game Engine: Clickteam Fusion 2.5<br><br>Item Drops powered by <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://steamworks.github.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Steamworks NET</a></a>",
